node.text: 25 years ago today the world lost a legend🙏🏽 Gone but never forgotten legends never die🥀 @2paclegacylives

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Mike Tyson | Boxing | Fan Page on September 13, 2021 tagging @miketyson. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
2002 - 2020🔥 18 years apart

“The boxing’s the easy part. When you get into the ring to fight that’s the vacation. But when you get in the gym, you have to do things over and over till you’re sore and deep in your mind you say, ‘I don’t want to do this anymore,’ I push that out of my mind.” -Mike Tyson

node.text:
"I hope I can improve. I'm far from perfect. Sometimes, I wonder what would happen if I fought myself. I think it would be a one-round KO. But if I was fighting myself, I know I could take my best punch. No, make that two rounds. I would knock myself out in two rounds” - Mike Tyson
Via @kingsmma_hb 🥊
